{
  "stem": "18258.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It-- there were 180,000 Jews in Vienna alone, 10% of the population.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "It couldn't happen.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Well, we were wrong.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And that was the Nazis immediately-- as soon as Hitler had taken over in '38 in an amazing, short time of a few days, he had really taken over Vienna and Austria.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We knew that, in the provinces, they were-- especially in the northern part in Tyrol, in upper Austria, in Vorarlberg, which is-- they were influenced.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They had contact with Germany.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Hitler supported the underground in Vienna actively with money and political support.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And many of the Christian socialists, the Vaterlandische Front-- which was the official organization of Schuschnigg and his predecessor, Dollfuss-- they were not at all very much opposed to the principles of the German Nazis.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Of course, after Dollfuss got killed by the Nazis and the party became legal, it was difficult.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "But the Nazis had grown strong.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And since the left wing-- the left-wing party was also suppressed, those who could afford it religion-wise joined them just out of pure opposition to the government.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had one of my friends who owned a motorcycle.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he once invited me if I want to join him on [NON-ENGLISH] on the-- [LAUGHS] on the back seat of his motorcycle for a two- or three-day trip to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Of course, I went along.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in Budapest, sightseeing, we went up to the, the Fisher Bastion and all over Budapest.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And at one spot, I noticed the swastika.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I went there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that was a fairly large poster.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I did-- I couldn't read it because it said, 'Eleg volt!' It didn't mean anything to me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I realized that Hungary already had been invaded, influenced, or infected by the bug.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
